"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-pressbox-press-releases-google-team-usa-and-nbcuniversal-strike-new-partnership-using-google-search-and-other-ai-powered-features-to-highlight-athlete-stories-and-enhance-nbcuniversals-coverage-of-olympic-and-paralympic-games-paris-2024\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Google Named the Official Search AI Partner of Team USA, Which Will Highlight How Search, Gemini and Google Maps Platform can help NBCUniversal viewers, Team USA fans, Olympians and Paralympians enjoy the Paris Games July 18, 2024 - New York, NY -Today, Google, Team USA and NBCUniversal announced a new partnership, with Google being named the Official Search AI Partner of Team USA, marking the first time the technology company has entered into a partnership with Team USA.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 155, \"end\": 163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999840838, \"rank\": 1.4201171968459774e-11, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 238, \"end\": 246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999994092142441, \"rank\": 5.905150662586751e-07, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 248, \"end\": 250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.274340834386849e-28, \"text\": \"NY\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 259, \"end\": 265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0038734897500667e-16, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wi