ion\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"just a sponsorship\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"a powerful alliance\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"technology\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By working with Google and NBCUniversal, we are ensuring that our athletes' stories are told in the most dynamic and engaging ways possible.\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 765, \"end\": 771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0038734897500667e-16, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 776, \"end\": 788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999766150725, \"rank\": 2.3385035329060483e-08, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our athletes' stories\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 832}, {\"ngram\": \"the most dynamic and engaging ways\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This partnership will inspire millions and amplify the incredible efforts of Team USA as they compete on the world stage.\\\"\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 1012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 967, \"end\": 975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999840838, \"rank\": 1.4201171968459774e-11, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This partnership\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"the incredible efforts\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 963}, {\"ngram\": \"the world stage\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Along with its partnership with Team USA, Google, in collaboration with NBCUniversal, will bring athlete stories and the competitions of the Paris Games to life by seamlessly integrating sponsored content formats - including ways to search and explore the Olympic & Paralympic Games with Google Search and related AI features - within NBCUniversal's extensive coverage.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999840838, \"rank\": 1.4201171968459774e-11, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1058, \"end\": 1064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0038734897500667e-16, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 1088, \"end\": 1100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999766150725, \"rank\": 2.3385035329060483e-08, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 1282, \"end\": 1298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.341031110170248e-13, \"text\": \"Paralympic Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\"}, {\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1807318370479396e-17, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 1351, \"end\": 1363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999766150725, \"rank\": 2.3385035329060483e-08, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its partnership\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"collaboration\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete stories\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1128}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitions\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1176}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsored content formats\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCUniversal's content will leverage Google's suite of consumer apps products, including Search, Maps and Gemini, as well as the advancements in each: \\u25cfExplain the Games with Google: NBCUniversal has created \\\"Explain the Games,\\\" which will showcase Google Search's AI Overviews and be used by NBCUniversal's award-winning production team and commentators during daytime and primetime coverage across all of NBCUniversal's Olympic linear networks and Peacock.\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1386, \"end\": 1398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.99999997